com.sg.util

Interface SGAgent.SGClient

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SGActivity
    Enclosing class:
    SGAgent

    public static interface SGAgent.SGClient
    SGClient interface. Defines methods to be implemented as SGAgent's client. These methods are called by SGAgent to notify Activity information or request Activity to do specified job.

      • onExtMethodNotification

        void onExtMethodNotification(String cookie,
                             int code,
                             String msg)
        Notify the result of asynchronous function.
        Parameters:
        cookie - string for identification passed when run the function
        code - result code. One of EXT_RET_OK, EXT_RET_ERROR and EXT_RET_CANCELLED.
        msg - content of notification. The format depends on function implementation.

      • onOrderInfoBegin

        boolean onOrderInfoBegin(int num)
        Inform client that order information notification will be started.
        Parameters:
        num - number of orders
        Returns:
        true for expecting SGAgent to send order information immediately, otherwise expecting SGAgent to send next order information every time SGAgent.wantOrderInfo() is called.

      • onOrderStateChange

        void onOrderStateChange(String productID,
                        String orderID,
                        String state)
        Notify client the state change of product purchase.
        Parameters:
        productID - product ID
        orderID - order ID
        state - state. One of the following text strings:
        "ordering" - generating order
        "ordered" - generated order
        "paying" - payment UI operation ongoing
        "cancelled" - cancelled by user
        "accepted" - payment request accepted by channel
        "confirming" - confirming order state
        "succeeded" - payment succeeded (money received)
        "cheated" - money is less than the price
        "failed" - payment failed
        "delivering" - (game server) marking order to be delivered
        "delivered" - (game server) marked order to be delivered

      • onProductBegin

        boolean onProductBegin(int num)
        Inform client that product information notification will be started.
        Parameters:
        num - number of products
        Returns:
        true for expecting SGAgent to send product information immediately, otherwise expecting SGAgent to send next product information every time SGAgent.wantProduct() is called.

      • onProductEnd

      • onStateChange

        void onStateChange(int type,
                   int orgState,
                   int newState,
                   int reason,
                   int op)
        Notify client the internal state change in SGAgent. You may use this notification to update UI or do relevant processing.
        Parameters:
        type - state type. One of STATE_TYPE_USR, STATE_TYPE_JOB and STATE_TYPE_PAY.
        orgState - original state
        newState - new state
        reason - reason of state change. One of STATE_CHANGE_REASON_NONE, STATE_CHANGE_REASON_OP, STATE_CHANGE_REASON_OP_SUCCESS, STATE_CHANGE_REASON_OP_FAILURE and STATE_CHANGE_REASON_OP_CANCELED.
        op - operation leading to the change

      • onTreasureChange

        void onTreasureChange(String name,
                      int count)
        Inform client updated treasure count.
        Parameters:
        name - treasure name
        count - treasure count

      • onTreasureListFound

        void onTreasureListFound(String[] treasures)
        Inform client that treasure list is retrieved.
        Parameters:
        treasures - Treasure array. Each item of the array has format "name=count", where 'count' is an integer indicating number of a certain treasure.
